name: G3G4 ThRee
description: Third installment of the collab between my son and I. These works were done on an app that my son loved to use when he was 2 years old. Like a true proud parent I saved his pieces in the hopes that I would be able to display them someday. This particular piece is combined with an original beat produced by me! The beat is dark and moody and is available as a full mp3 once the NFT is purchased.
